data.description: Be sure to watch the video to view this wonderful condo & surrounding community! Exclusive area, exclusive lifestyle! This immaculate, well cared for condo is located in the sought after area of the Belleview Biltmore community, tucked back alongside the Belleview Inn and Belleair Country Club.  Minutes from downtown Belleair Bluffs which boasts great restaurants, shopping and close to beach access. This two bedroom, two bath condo was completely remodeled in 2019/2020 barely lived in. Unit offers new impact windows, solar remote shades in all exposed rooms and Dan’s fans just to mention a few items! Unit offers Northwest exposure which allows you to see Downtown Clearwater, the Memorial Causeway, Clearwater Beach, the Sand Key Bridge and part of Sand Key.  Views include Clearwater Bay and the Gulf of Mexico. The living room and both bedrooms lead to the balcony area.  This unit also has its own full size washer and dryer in laundry closet, newer water heater and A/C. The pool area has a new heater and chiller for those hot summer days, 24-hour guarded security gate for peace of mind and safety. The country club offers social memberships which include fine dining, a fitness center, tennis courts, pickle ball courts and so much more. As an owner in the community you also do not have to wait to become a golf member of the Belleair Country Club (multi-year wait). Enjoy the prestigious two 18-hole golf courses designed by Donald Ross.
